  "body": "I'm not sure if others are experiencing this, but when running beta8.rc1 (packaged build from CI) on my Windows 10 laptop, after I close the app it turns into a zombie process and I need to manually kill the process using Task Manager. If the process isn't manually killed then after restarting the app it's not possible to login because the zombie app/status-go has control of the database.",
